Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:09.96,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:22.89,Base,,0,0,0,,That's not... why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:25.44,Base,,0,0,0,,I just wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.94,Base,,0,0,0,,...to apologize to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.50,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tears Overwritten"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.96,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.55,Base,,0,0,0,,I left Watanabe-san with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:22.89,Base,,0,0,0,,It's my fault Naracchi\Nwas forced to quit JPX.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.72,Base,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:33.15,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not Ai-chan, but if you want,\NI can hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.86,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, I {\i1}am {\i0}her room--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa! No sharing personal information!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.16,Base,,0,0,0,,Narata-sensei?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:44.58,Base,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to let the two of you\Ngo by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Who knew if this guy was a total perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.96,Base,,0,0,0,,A... total perv?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.13,Base,,0,0,0,,He's not a perv, he's a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.04,Base,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:59.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Perv, stalker, call me whatever you want.\NIt's my fault, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.60,Base,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan might've told me\Nthat we weren't friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:14.77,Base,,0,0,0,,but that really sucks, and I still want\Nto try to be friends with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:19.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Could you please tell me what happened\Nbetween you two, Mister Stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:33.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Sarasa Watanabe's with a guy?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, he's so ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.17,Base,,0,0,0,,But I guess she {\i1}would {\i0}be into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.88,Base,,0,0,0,,--Here.\N--Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:42.88,Base,,0,0,0,,--Wait, Narata-sensei's there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.76,Base,,0,0,0,,--Thank you!\N--Wait, Narata-sensei's there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.52,Base,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:55.15,Base,,0,0,0,,I used to be an unemployed shut-in\Nwho never left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mister Shut-In!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:02.74,Base,,0,0,0,,I was never good with people,\Nso I started ditching school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:06.99,Base,,0,0,0,,I spent every day watching anime,\Nplaying games, and browsing the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:10.50,Base,,0,0,0,,I love anime, too! I'm super into\N{\i1}Floor Kings {\i0}right no--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.00,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let him talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:20.51,Base,,0,0,0,,One day, I had this music show on, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.97,Base,,0,0,0,,What?! Who {\i1}is {\i0}this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:28.10,Base,,0,0,0,,And why does she try so hard\Nto never, ever smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.68,Base,,0,0,0,,It hit me like a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.31,Base,,0,0,0,,She didn't seem scared, or shy, or lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.19,Base,,0,0,0,,She reminded me of a fantasy princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.02,Base,,0,0,0,,or an ice queen singing\Nabout letting things go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.15,Base,,0,0,0,,But then, there was that fateful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:47.41,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Local Mascot Meet n' Greet"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:47.41,Base,,0,0,0,,Today, we've brought a bunch of your\Nfavorite local mascots to meet the JPX48!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Today, we've brought a bunch of your\Nfavorite local mascots to meet the JPX48!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Which is your favorite, Komomo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:55.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, I think I like\NStarry Boy the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:59.50,Base,,0,0,0,,I knew 100% she'd fallen from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.92,Base,,0,0,0,,That day, June 23rd, the Naracchi Nation\Nopened to one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"ANONYMOUS: WELCOME TO\NTHE NARACCHI NATION"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.55,Base,,0,0,0,,That day, June 23rd, the Naracchi Nation\Nopened to one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.38,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"ANONYMOUS: She's kinda cute"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Like when Commodore Perry came to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.81,Base,,0,0,0,,That's when I knew... I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.89,Base,,0,0,0,,I wanted to open my borders, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.11,Base,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to worry about\Nwhat others thought of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.44,Base,,0,0,0,,I could just be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.74,Base,,0,0,0,,A fellow Naracchi stan, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:34.16,Base,,0,0,0,,I made friends and got a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:34.50,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"JPX48 Handshake Event"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:34.50,Base,,0,0,0,,I made friends and got a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.17,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"JPX48 Handshake Event"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Please line up only after double-checking\Nthe number on your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:37.87,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ai Narata"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:37.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Please line up only after double-checking\Nthe number on your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ai Narata"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.88,Base,,0,0,0,,How can I tell her\Nhow much she means to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.34,Base,,0,0,0,,How can I tell her\Nhow much she means to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:45.13,Base,,0,0,0,,...in the brief moment\Nwe'll share together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:52.10,Base,,0,0,0,,I have to thank you. I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.52,Base,,0,0,0,,I have to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.61,Base,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Naracchi, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.69,Base,,0,0,0,,--I love you!\N--Hey, sir--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.41,Base,,0,0,0,,Let go, creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.70,Base,,0,0,0,,It took so long to crawl my way up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.87,Base,,0,0,0,,but only a second to fall back\Nto the pits of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:20.67,Base,,0,0,0,,That's when I remembered the truth.\NI'm just a gross otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.67,Base,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Mister Gross Otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.88,Base,,0,0,0,,You poor guy! Cheer up,\NMister Gross Otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.47,Base,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay, I'm over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.14,Base,,0,0,0,,But to make up for it,\NNaracchi was forced to graduate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.39,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"RIP Naracchi lmao"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.39,Base,,0,0,0,,"does she hate her fans??" "GJ Naracchi."\NBut to make up for it,\NNaracchi was forced to graduate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.31,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"RIP Naracchi lmao"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.31,Base,,0,0,0,,"does she hate her fans??" "GJ Naracchi."\Nwithout even a special event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.39,Base,,0,0,0,,And all because I held onto\NNaracchi's hand for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.98,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ai Narata EXPELLED from JPX"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.98,Base,,0,0,0,,And all because I held onto\NNaracchi's hand for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.40,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ai Narata EXPELLED from JPX"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.40,Base,,0,0,0,,But I was just one guy. There wasn't\Nanything I could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:47.61,Base,,0,0,0,,But I was just one guy. There wasn't\Nanything I could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.20,Base,,0,0,0,,I knew it might've been selfish of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.03,Base,,0,0,0,,but I wanted to at least\Napologize to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:58.54,Base,,0,0,0,,But that probably just makes me\Neven more of a creep to Naracchi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:02.54,Base,,0,0,0,,You don't seem like a bad person.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, Creepy Otaku Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure, just call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:12.68,Base,,0,0,0,,So I've got good news and bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:17.27,Base,,0,0,0,,The good news is that Ai\Ndoesn't hate you specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.56,Base,,0,0,0,,She gets creeped out by every man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.81,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.02,Base,,0,0,0,,What probably happened is she'd been holding\Nback for the whole handshaking event
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.15,Base,,0,0,0,,and just happened to break\Nwhen it was your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Now for the bad news:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:35.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai isn't as attached to JPX as you hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I can probably say the same\Nthing about her and the Kouka Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.04,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tear Spray"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.04,Base,,0,0,0,,At some point, Ai gave up on the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:45.13,Base,,0,0,0,,At some point, Ai gave up on the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:49.30,Base,,0,0,0,,and started hiding her emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:54.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Right now, she's just trying to find a\Nplace where she can relax and feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:08:01.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Dealing with people is annoying\Nand a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.77,Base,,0,0,0,,But she has so much potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.36,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, the first time I saw Ai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:11.24,Base,,0,0,0,,I thought she looked like Alice\Nstumbling into Wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:13.45,Base,,0,0,0,,"How perfect for Kouka," I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.37,Base,,0,0,0,,She would be the type of person\Nto stand and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:17.78,Base,,0,0,0,,in the center of the Kouka stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:26.46,Base,,0,0,0,,I knew I wanted to stand up\Non that stage with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Narata-san, where are you going?\NIt's almost time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san's not back yet.\NI'm going to go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.68,Base,,0,0,0,,I saw her alone with a guy earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.64,Base,,0,0,0,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.31,Base,,0,0,0,,What a great pic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:48.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Now, what should I do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.53,Base,,0,0,0,,She's not here. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.78,Base,,0,0,0,,What if he did something to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.75,Base,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.38,Base,,0,0,0,,You're not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.55,Base,,0,0,0,,I am a rising Kouka star, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.06,Base,,0,0,0,,Well then, can you do {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.31,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Matrix!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:40.20,Base,,0,0,0,,You came back! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.45,Base,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.12,Base,,0,0,0,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.92,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...hate you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.21,Base,,0,0,0,,You... hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:09.48,Base,,0,0,0,,My goodness! I can barely\Nhear you, Watanabe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.94,Base,,0,0,0,,Usually you're far too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.36,Base,,0,0,0,,You need to sing a little\Nlouder, too, Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.07,Base,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:20.82,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm on a diet right now,\Nso I don't have the energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:24.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, that's good,\Nbut take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:25.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's split into quartets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, Hoshino-san,\NNarata-san, and Watanabe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.43,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you got so mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me why you got angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:54.40,Base,,0,0,0,,Uh... Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:57.82,Base,,0,0,0,,If I tell you, will you finally\Nleave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:05.08,Base,,0,0,0,,I felt horrible for running off\Nand leaving you there with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:09.12,Base,,0,0,0,,It took everything I had just to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.58,Base,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Believe what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:19.05,Base,,0,0,0,,You and Taichi and that guy\Nwere dancing around like {\i1}idiots{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.89,Base,,0,0,0,,that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:29.31,Base,,0,0,0,,If you came back 'cause you were worried\Nabout me, then you should've been happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:35.36,Base,,0,0,0,,If you were worried, you should've\Nbeen glad to see I was okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:38.15,Base,,0,0,0,,You're just trying to pick a fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Just don't bother me anymore, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.91,Base,,0,0,0,,Fine, then! We're {\i1}through{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Nothing's through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.41,Base,,0,0,0,,I told you, we {\i1}aren't friends{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:06.10,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sarasa"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:12.10,Base,,0,0,0,,I told a girl I wanted to be\Nfriends with that "we're through."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.98,Base,,0,0,0,,How dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:18.40,Base,,0,0,0,,But I still won't start to hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:23.28,Base,,0,0,0,,She has so many qualities I admire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.07,Base,,0,0,0,,I can't help but look up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:35.46,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't feel like you have to rush.\NYou're just getting to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Just take your time and keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:42.76,Base,,0,0,0,,But remember, you might not\Nget what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:47.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Your feelings may be one-sided in the end,\Nand you'll have to look on from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:51.10,Base,,0,0,0,,But I think that's beautiful\Nin its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:54.31,Base,,0,0,0,,One-sided feelings are beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:57.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Akiya-kun is so poetic sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:02.69,Base,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Kouzaburou! Stop tweeting\Nand pretending to be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.28,Base,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be too heavy\Nfor you to handle, Akiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.21,Base,,0,0,0,,Let her be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.76,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Narata-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:34.43,Base,,0,0,0,,I can't find Ai. Have you seen her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:38.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, I assumed she felt bad\Nand went back to the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Is she actually skipping class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.57,Base,,0,0,0,,I hope that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:44.32,Base,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like\Nshe went back to the dorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.28,Base,,0,0,0,,and she's not picking up her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:51.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai's not the type to wander around town,\Neither, 'cause of how she sticks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:55.16,Base,,0,0,0,,And she wouldn't want to give strangers\Nany reason to talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:58.17,Base,,0,0,0,,so she's likely not breaking any rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.\NI'll keep looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:05.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Um, do you think she might've been feeling\Nhomesick and went back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:08.30,Base,,0,0,0,,I really doubt that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.22,Base,,0,0,0,,Could we borrow you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:27.20,Base,,0,0,0,,I wish Watanabe-san\Nwould drop out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hold up,\Nisn't that Naracchi from JPX?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Yo, it totally is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Holy shit, she's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Where is Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Did she run away because\NI said we were through?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.05,Base,,0,0,0,,No way, she wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.92,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.63,Base,,0,0,0,,This is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:49.93,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"That's a Kouka student, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:49.93,Base,,0,0,0,,This is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.89,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"That's a Kouka student, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's me! It's totally me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.02,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I thought their school rules\Nwere stricter than this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.02,Base,,0,0,0,,And they've blacked out my eyes\Nlike I'm a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.60,Base,,0,0,0,,So you admit it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.35,Base,,0,0,0,,--That's you and your boyfriend?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.86,Base,,0,0,0,,The Kouka Troupe does allow\Nromantic relationships,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.53,Base,,0,0,0,,but you can't be so open about it that\Nothers can get a picture of you two alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Especially when you're still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:12.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, but we weren't alone!\NNarata-sensei was with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.49,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll talk to him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:21.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. If this gets out, I'm sure a few\Nsecond-years will have it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.29,Base,,0,0,0,,But I guess your boyfriend is worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.59,Base,,0,0,0,,He's not my boyfriend, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:33.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Senpai,\Ncan we continue this later?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.02,Base,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something\Nsuper important I gotta do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.27,Base,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.65,Base,,0,0,0,,You took it {\i1}way {\i0}too far this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.57,Base,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me or something, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.16,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Call from Sarasa Watanabe"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm still in Kobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Naracchi's in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.55,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm bored of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:10.51,Base,,0,0,0,,I've never skipped school before, so I\Ndon't know what I'm supposed to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:16.47,Base,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they noticed I'm gone,\Nor if they're even worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, 'scuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.64,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda lost. Could you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:27.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hold up, are you Naracchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Can I get a selfie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Let go, you creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.20,Base,,0,0,0,,--Yo, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:36.41,Base,,0,0,0,,--Why is it so hard for me\Nto live in this world?\N--Yo, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:41.04,Base,,0,0,0,,--Why is it so hard for me\Nto live in this world?\N--He just wanted a selfie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:44.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.42,Base,,0,0,0,,No. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop that, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Get your dirty paws...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:03.77,Base,,0,0,0,,...off of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.65,Base,,0,0,0,,What the shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.11,Base,,0,0,0,,She obviously wants you to go away!\NShe told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.40,Base,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--I'm not scared of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.82,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of you {\i1}or {\i0}you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.95,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... what do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.16,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she really was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:32.63,Base,,0,0,0,,I said we were through, Ai-chan,\Nbut I'll help you just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Just this once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:43.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Help! These guys won't leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.27,Base,,0,0,0,,She's so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.02,Base,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.06,Base,,0,0,0,,And she's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:51.90,Base,,0,0,0,,These guys are harassing\Ntwo sweet, innocent girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Shit, cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Fine, we'll let you\Noff the hook this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.03,Base,,0,0,0,,Weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.12,Base,,0,0,0,,You heard her! You're coming\Nto the station with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're a teacher at Kouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:18.68,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes. My name is Taichi Narata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:21.39,Base,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Otaku figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.23,Base,,0,0,0,,I got his number before he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.31,Base,,0,0,0,,The ocean! She's gotta be near the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:36.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Y'see, in the March 2018 issue of POCO mag\Nand the JPX official newsletter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.53,Base,,0,0,0,,she said the ocean makes her feel calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.12,Base,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really\Nnarrow it down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.79,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll do a search on social media!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.96,Base,,0,0,0,,This is bad. I gotta find her...\NI gotta find her, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:54.59,Base,,0,0,0,,And then he really {\i1}did {\i0}find you!\NIsn't that awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:59.22,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Otaku really\Ncares about you, Ai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san, could you tell them\Nyour side of the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:21.70,Base,,0,0,0,,Here. Wipe your face with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:42.47,Base,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:53.44,Base,,0,0,0,,This is the best I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.28,Base,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:01.36,Base,,0,0,0,,Really, it's okay. Please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:06.99,Base,,0,0,0,,I... no, {\i1}we {\i0}only ever wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:10.46,Base,,0,0,0,,to see you smile, Naracchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.13,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever\Nget this close to you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:17.67,Base,,0,0,0,,so please let me keep your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.17,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for scaring you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:25.18,Base,,0,0,0,,One day, I'll come see you perform\Non the big Kouka stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:28.77,Base,,0,0,0,,When that day comes, I hope I'll see\Nyour beautiful smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:30.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.19,Base,,0,0,0,,And thank you. Until we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:49.87,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hana no Michi: Flower Way"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.37,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hana no Michi: Flower Way"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Mister Creepy Otaku was a pretty nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:58.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, and his real name is\NMikiya Kitaouji! It sounds so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:03.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, if there's something\NI want to forget, but can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.05,Base,,0,0,0,,what should I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:11.02,Base,,0,0,0,,Not surprised. Anybody would be weirded\Nout by a random question like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:17.06,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm only 15, so there's a lot\NI have to learn about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:19.02,Base,,0,0,0,,But even if you can't forget\Nsomething that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:21.94,Base,,0,0,0,,you can make new memories by having fun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.86,Base,,0,0,0,,and being passionate about\Nthe things you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:27.95,Base,,0,0,0,,Just keep overwriting the bad memories\Nwith lots of good ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:32.50,Base,,0,0,0,,and eventually,\Nthe bad ones will fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Because I was walking behind her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:40.00,Base,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see the expression\Non her face when she said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:43.42,Base,,0,0,0,,When we got back,\Nthe second-years were waiting for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.18,Base,,0,0,0,,and for the following week,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:50.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san and I had our\Nmorning cleaning hours doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:39.96,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Act 5: The Chosen Maidens"
